JAVASCRIPT REQUIREMENTS
═══════════════════════════════════════
- Tab switching: show/hide page divs, toggle active class on tab buttons
- Count-up animation on .count-up elements (data-target attribute) 
  using setInterval, triggers on page load
- Charts only initialize when their tab is first activated (lazy init), 
  track with a `charts` object to avoid re-creating
- All chart data defined inline in JS, no fetch calls
- Charts use Chart.js 4.4.1 from cdnjs

Output: one complete .html file, all CSS in <style>, all JS in <script>.
No comments needed. Make it work perfectly.